com.foreach.across.modules.entity.views.bootstrapui.options

Class EnumOptionIterableBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.modules.entity.views.bootstrapui.options.EnumOptionIterableBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OptionIterableBuilder

    public class EnumOptionIterableBuilder
extends Object
implements OptionIterableBuilder
    Generates OptionFormElementBuilders for an enum. Requires an EntityMessageCodeResolver attribute to be present when building. A message code of the form enums.ENUM_NAME.ENUM_VALUE will be looked up.

    An EnumOptionIterableBuilder is never sorted.

    Author:
    Arne Vandamme
